Class MapRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • bean.pwr.imskamieskiego.repository.MapRepository
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMapRepository

    public class MapRepository
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMapRepository
    This class is implementation of IMapRepository. It should be used to get access to data related to map location ect. Methods of this class must be call from thread other than main thread.
